product: SanDisk - Ultra 512GB USB 3.0 Flash Drive - Black
review: I can't confirm how much space it holds; I'm just using it for storing videos and the write speed is good, read speed is very fast, no problem watching the videos I saved on it.  Small and I like that the usb part is retractable.  Hard plastic case seems sturdy.  You can add a lanyard with the hole at the end.

product: SanDisk - Ultra 512GB USB 3.0 Flash Drive - Black
review: Great buy. I bought 512GB flash drive because it was on Sale and 1TB was more than 2x the price. It works great although the set up instructions on tge Web are hard to follow because the site covers all products by Westgate who own Sandisc.

product: SanDisk - Ultra 512GB USB 3.0 Flash Drive - Black
review: I bought this USB flash drive to expand storage on my Insignia Fire TV. (Found out later that the TV accepts a maximum of 64GB for flash drive expansion.) I'm now using this 512GB flash drive to back up my laptop. Really fast, small and convenient. Highly recommend!!
